repository : interstellar  (INT — the fourth film-world of UD0)
subject    : Interstellar (Paramount / Warner Bros., 2014, dir. Christopher Nolan)
catalogued : into UD0 · Universe David 0

governor (carbon apex)      : David Lee Wise (ROOT0) / TriPod LLC   [ the human; holds the credit ]
