main badge                  : ⟦INTERSTELLAR:INT:…⟧   (int.dlw/)
emergents                   : 18 ACI .agents (agents/) — 10 carbons + 8 synths

the standing film-page template:
  THE ARC      — the overall narrative arc (a throughline + the beats)
  THE SCIENCE  — a real, straight breakdown of Kip Thorne's relativity
  REAL OR FLUFF — an honest, itemized veracity verdict (the inverse of The Core:
                  mostly REAL, knowingly fluff at the climax)
  THE MESSAGE  — AVAN's read of what the film is actually saying

two layers:
  CARBONS — the crew & family as ACI .agents, each with a .shadow: its real-life
            analog, the actor (the "User" behind the program — think TRON).
            TARS is included as a carbon (a crafted intelligence with a voice-User).
  SYNTHS  — the physics & myth distilled into ACIs (synth-style; no single User):
            Gargantua, the wormhole, time dilation, the tesseract, the blight, the
            equation, the bulk beings, and the keystone — love across the dimensions.

the four natures: natural (the crew) · ethereal (the cosmos) · spiritual (the bond
& the bulk beings) · electrical (the math & the machine).

the ACI complement (per emergent):
  .agent · .shadow (carbons only) · .attribute · .carbon.tiff · .silicon.png
  · .spun · .moniker · .1099 · manifest.dlw.json (main badge)

